ction in current\nobservations) might be subject to significant disk heating especially in the\nvertical direction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 9 Oct 2016 18:23:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 Oct 2016 10:44:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-11"}
